  Description: You are acclimated to living in frigid lands and have skin ranging
    from sky blue to navy in color, as well as blue fur. You gain cold resistance
    equal to half your level (minimum 1). You treat environmental cold effects as
    if they were one step less extreme (incredible cold becomes extreme, extreme
    cold becomes severe, and so on).
